title: Roger Miller - Best Of Roger Miller  (FLAC)
description:
Best of Roger Miller: His Greatest Songs is an 11-track budget-priced collection that features some of his biggest hits, emphasizing such humorous tunes as "King of the Road," "Dang Me," "Chug-A-Lug," "Do-Wacka-Do," "Kansas City Star," and "You Can't Roller Skate in a Buffalo Herd."





1 King Of The Road
2 Dang Me
3 Chug-a-lug
4 Engine, Engine #9
5 England Swings
6 Do-Wacka-Do
7 Husbands And Wives
8 You Don't Want My Love
9 Me and Bobby McGee
10 When Two Worlds Collide
11 Kansas City Star
12 You Can't Roller Skate in a Buffalo Herd
